{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0124azYK8Wtfz2ELawru8XZy","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package quarkus.tutorial.order.web;\n     2→\n     3→import io.quarkus.qute.Template;\n     4→import io.quarkus.qute.TemplateInstance;\n     5→import jakarta.inject.Inject;\n     6→import jakarta.ws.rs.*;\n     7→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.MediaType;\n     8→import java.util.List;\n     9→\n    10→@Path(\"/\")\n    11→public class OrderWebController {\n    12→\n    13→    @Inject\n    14→    OrderController orderController;\n    15→\n    16→    @Inject\n    17→    Template orders;\n    18→\n    19→    @Inject\n    20→    Template lineItems;\n    21→\n    22→    @GET\n    23→    @Path(\"/orders\")\n    24→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    25→    public TemplateInstance getOrders(@QueryParam(\"vendorName\") String vendorName, @QueryParam(\"vendorSearchResults\") List<String> vendorSearchResults) {\n    26→        return orders.data(\"orders\", orderController.getOrders())\n    27→                     .data(\"vendorName\", vendorName)\n    28→                     .data(\"vendorSearchResults\", vendorSearchResults)\n    29→                     .data(\"findVendorTableDisabled\", vendorSearchResults != null);\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    @POST\n    33→    @Path(\"/submitOrder\")\n    34→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    35→    public TemplateInstance submitOrder(\n    36→            @FormParam(\"newOrderId\") Integer newOrderId,\n    37→            @FormParam(\"newOrderStatus\") String newOrderStatus,\n    38→            @FormParam(\"newOrderDiscount\") int newOrderDiscount,\n    39→            @FormParam(\"newOrderShippingInfo\") String newOrderShippingInfo) {\n    40→        orderController.submitOrder(newOrderId, newOrderStatus.charAt(0), newOrderDiscount, newOrderShippingInfo);\n    41→        return orders.data(\"orders\", orderController.getOrders())\n    42→                     .data(\"vendorName\", null)\n    43→                     .data(\"vendorSearchResults\", null)\n    44→                     .data(\"findVendorTableDisabled\", false);\n    45→    }\n    46→\n    47→    @POST\n    48→    @Path(\"/removeOrder\")\n    49→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    50→    public TemplateInstance removeOrder(@FormParam(\"orderId\") Integer orderId) {\n    51→        orderController.removeOrder(orderId);\n    52→        return orders.data(\"orders\", orderController.getOrders())\n    53→                     .data(\"vendorName\", null)\n    54→                     .data(\"vendorSearchResults\", null)\n    55→                     .data(\"findVendorTableDisabled\", false);\n    56→    }\n    57→\n    58→    @GET\n    59→    @Path(\"/lineItems\")\n    60→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    61→    public TemplateInstance getLineItems(@QueryParam(\"orderId\") Integer orderId) {\n    62→        return lineItems.data(\"currentOrder\", orderId)\n    63→                        .data(\"lineItems\", orderController.getLineItems(orderId))\n    64→                        .data(\"newOrderParts\", orderController.getNewOrderParts());\n    65→    }\n    66→\n    67→    @POST\n    68→    @Path(\"/addLineItem\")\n    69→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    70→    public TemplateInstance addLineItem(\n    71→            @FormParam(\"currentOrder\") Integer currentOrder,\n    72→            @FormParam(\"selectedPartNumber\") String selectedPartNumber,\n    73→            @FormParam(\"selectedPartRevision\") int selectedPartRevision) {\n    74→        orderController.addLineItem(currentOrder, selectedPartNumber, selectedPartRevision);\n    75→        return lineItems.data(\"currentOrder\", currentOrder)\n    76→                        .data(\"lineItems\", orderController.getLineItems(currentOrder))\n    77→                        .data(\"newOrderParts\", orderController.getNewOrderParts());\n    78→    }\n    79→\n    80→    @POST\n    81→    @Path(\"/findVendor\")\n    82→    @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_HTML)\n    83→    public TemplateInstance findVendor(@FormParam(\"vendorName\") String vendorName) {\n    84→        return orders.data(\"orders\", orderController.getOrders())\n    85→                     .data(\"vendorName\", vendorName)\n    86→                     .data(\"vendorSearchResults\", orderController.findVendor(vendorName))\n    87→                     .data(\"findVendorTableDisabled\", true);\n    88→    }\n    89→}\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015SpBXrAf2izpCWK8tU3TqS","session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"71a59de2-f70d-41d1-9d1a-a4c631ef66df"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-3-5-haiku-20241022","id":"msg_bdrk_01DmiL7h9MLt1tPSXRteReGM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01USzFG9RWVzXd6KZ9KC3kBR","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__order__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/resources/templates/orders.html"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1554,"cache_read_input_tokens":18271,"output_tokens":114},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015SpBXrAf2izpCWK8tU3TqS","session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"c9cd3a6b-dab3-4176-8224-07f10fda6b78"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01USzFG9RWVzXd6KZ9KC3kBR","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!DOCTYPE html>\n     2→<html>\n     3→<head>\n     4→    <title>Order Java Persistence Example</title>\n     5→</head>\n     6→<body>\n     7→    {#include orderTemplate}\n     8→        {#title}Order Java Persistence Example{/title}\n     9→        {#ordersTable}\n    10→        <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    11→            <tr>\n    12→                <th>Order ID</th>\n    13→                <th>Shipment Info</th>\n    14→                <th>Status</th>\n    15→                <th>Last Updated</th>\n    16→                <th>Discount</th>\n    17→                <th>Actions</th>\n    18→            </tr>\n    19→            {#for order in orders}\n    20→            <tr>\n    21→                <td>\n    22→                    <a href=\"/lineItems?orderId={order.orderId}\">{order.orderId}</a>\n    23→                </td>\n    24→                <td>{order.shipmentInfo}</td>\n    25→                <td>{order.status}</td>\n    26→                <td>{order.lastUpdate}</td>\n    27→                <td>{order.discount}%</td>\n    28→                <td>\n    29→                    <form method=\"post\" action=\"/removeOrder\">\n    30→                        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"orderId\" value=\"{order.orderId}\"/>\n    31→                        <button type=\"submit\">Delete</button>\n    32→                    </form>\n    33→                </td>\n    34→            </tr>\n    35→            {/for}\n    36→        </table>\n    37→        {/ordersTable}\n    38→        {#newOrderForm}\n    39→        <form method=\"post\" action=\"/submitOrder\">\n    40→            <label for=\"orderIdInputText\">Order ID: </label>\n    41→            <input type=\"number\" id=\"orderIdInputText\" name=\"newOrderId\" required/><br/>\n    42→            <label for=\"shipmentInfoInputText\">Shipment Info: </label>\n    43→            <input type=\"text\" id=\"shipmentInfoInputText\" name=\"newOrderShippingInfo\" required/><br/>\n    44→            <label for=\"statusMenu\">Status: </label>\n    45→            <select id=\"statusMenu\" name=\"newOrderStatus\" required>\n    46→                <option value=\"Y\">Complete</option>\n    47→                <option value=\"N\">Pending</option>\n    48→            </select><br/>\n    49→            <label for=\"discountMenu\">Discount: </label>\n    50→            <select id=\"discountMenu\" name=\"newOrderDiscount\" required>\n    51→                <option value=\"0\">0 %</option>\n    52→                <option value=\"5\">5 %</option>\n    53→                <option value=\"10\">10 %</option>\n    54→                <option value=\"15\">15 %</option>\n    55→                <option value=\"20\">20 %</option>\n    56→                <option value=\"25\">25 %</option>\n    57→                <option value=\"30\">30 %</option>\n    58→                <option value=\"35\">35 %</option>\n    59→                <option value=\"40\">40 %</option>\n    60→            </select><br/>\n    61→            <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n    62→        </form>\n    63→        {/newOrderForm}\n    64→        {#findVendorForm}\n    65→        <form method=\"post\" action=\"/findVendor\">\n    66→            <label for=\"findVendorInputText\">Search for Vendors: </label>\n    67→            <input type=\"text\" id=\"findVendorInputText\" name=\"vendorName\" value=\"{vendorName ?: ''}\" required/>\n    68→            <button type=\"submit\" id=\"findVendorButton\">Find Vendor</button>\n    69→        </form>\n    70→        {/findVendorForm}\n    71→        {#findVendorTable}\n    72→        {#if findVendorTableDisabled}\n    73→        <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    74→            <tr><th>Vendor</th></tr>\n    75→            {#for vendor in vendorSearchResults}\n    76→            <tr><td>{vendor}</td></tr>\n    77→            {/for}\n    78→        </table>\n    79→        {/if}\n    80→        {/findVendorTable}\n    81→    {/include}\n    82→</body>\n    83→</html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015SpBXrAf2izpCWK8tU3TqS","session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"b5377bfe-b8e1-475d-8361-1da871caeed6"}
