{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GSzFTrANBJS9YgvpsFQBN5","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!DOCTYPE html>\n     2→<html>\n     3→<head>\n     4→    <title>Order Java Persistence Example</title>\n     5→</head>\n     6→<body>\n     7→    {#include orderTemplate}\n     8→        {#title}Order Java Persistence Example{/title}\n     9→        {#ordersTable}\n    10→        <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    11→            <tr>\n    12→                <th>Order ID</th>\n    13→                <th>Shipment Info</th>\n    14→                <th>Status</th>\n    15→                <th>Last Updated</th>\n    16→                <th>Discount</th>\n    17→                <th>Actions</th>\n    18→            </tr>\n    19→            {#for order in orders}\n    20→            <tr>\n    21→                <td>\n    22→                    <a href=\"/lineItems?orderId={order.orderId}\">{order.orderId}</a>\n    23→                </td>\n    24→                <td>{order.shipmentInfo}</td>\n    25→                <td>{order.status}</td>\n    26→                <td>{order.lastUpdate}</td>\n    27→                <td>{order.discount}%</td>\n    28→                <td>\n    29→                    <form method=\"post\" action=\"/removeOrder\">\n    30→                        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"orderId\" value=\"{order.orderId}\"/>\n    31→                        <button type=\"submit\">Delete</button>\n    32→                    </form>\n    33→                </td>\n    34→            </tr>\n    35→            {/for}\n    36→        </table>\n    37→        {/ordersTable}\n    38→        {#newOrderForm}\n    39→        <form method=\"post\" action=\"/submitOrder\">\n    40→            <label for=\"orderIdInputText\">Order ID: </label>\n    41→            <input type=\"number\" id=\"orderIdInputText\" name=\"newOrderId\" required/><br/>\n    42→            <label for=\"shipmentInfoInputText\">Shipment Info: </label>\n    43→            <input type=\"text\" id=\"shipmentInfoInputText\" name=\"newOrderShippingInfo\" required/><br/>\n    44→            <label for=\"statusMenu\">Status: </label>\n    45→            <select id=\"statusMenu\" name=\"newOrderStatus\" required>\n    46→                <option value=\"Y\">Complete</option>\n    47→                <option value=\"N\">Pending</option>\n    48→            </select><br/>\n    49→            <label for=\"discountMenu\">Discount: </label>\n    50→            <select id=\"discountMenu\" name=\"newOrderDiscount\" required>\n    51→                <option value=\"0\">0 %</option>\n    52→                <option value=\"5\">5 %</option>\n    53→                <option value=\"10\">10 %</option>\n    54→                <option value=\"15\">15 %</option>\n    55→                <option value=\"20\">20 %</option>\n    56→                <option value=\"25\">25 %</option>\n    57→                <option value=\"30\">30 %</option>\n    58→                <option value=\"35\">35 %</option>\n    59→                <option value=\"40\">40 %</option>\n    60→            </select><br/>\n    61→            <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n    62→        </form>\n    63→        {/newOrderForm}\n    64→        {#findVendorForm}\n    65→        <form method=\"post\" action=\"/findVendor\">\n    66→            <label for=\"findVendorInputText\">Search for Vendors: </label>\n    67→            <input type=\"text\" id=\"findVendorInputText\" name=\"vendorName\" value=\"{vendorName ?: ''}\" required/>\n    68→            <button type=\"submit\" id=\"findVendorButton\">Find Vendor</button>\n    69→        </form>\n    70→        {/findVendorForm}\n    71→        {#findVendorTable}\n    72→        {#if findVendorTableDisabled}\n    73→        <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    74→            <tr><th>Vendor</th></tr>\n    75→            {#for vendor in vendorSearchResults}\n    76→            <tr><td>{vendor}</td></tr>\n    77→            {/for}\n    78→        </table>\n    79→        {/if}\n    80→        {/findVendorTable}\n    81→    {/include}\n    82→</body>\n    83→</html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"2b5268b2-3ed6-4bc5-952b-f96bdfc618fe"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_019NPJ5xZnQg9hmnKPr3NNry","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!DOCTYPE html>\n     2→<html lang=\"en\">\n     3→<head>\n     4→    <title>{#insert title}Default Title{/insert}</title>\n     5→    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/default.css\"/>\n     6→</head>\n     7→<body>\n     8→    <h1>{#insert title}Default Title{/insert}</h1>\n     9→\n    10→    {#insert body}Default Body{/insert}\n    11→\n    12→    <h2>View All Orders</h2>\n    13→    {#insert ordersTable}Default ordersTable{/insert}\n    14→\n    15→    <h2>Create New Order</h2>\n    16→    {#insert newOrderForm}Default new orders form{/insert}\n    17→\n    18→    <h2>Find Vendors</h2>\n    19→    {#insert findVendorForm}Default find vendors form{/insert}\n    20→\n    21→    {#insert findVendorTable}Default find vendor table{/insert}\n    22→</body>\n    23→</html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"3a5fba15-1edb-4ecf-9994-997aba0edb22"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01M4QiWEZDe3rRcDZjLjUiEi","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!DOCTYPE html>\n     2→<html>\n     3→<head>\n     4→    <title>Line Items for Order {currentOrder}</title>\n     5→</head>\n     6→<body>\n     7→    {#include lineItemTemplate}\n     8→        {#title}Line Items for Order {currentOrder}{/title}\n     9→        {#body}\n    10→        <form method=\"post\">\n    11→            <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    12→                <tr>\n    13→                    <th>Item ID</th>\n    14→                    <th>Quantity</th>\n    15→                    <th>Vendor Part Number</th>\n    16→                </tr>\n    17→                {#for lineItem in lineItems}\n    18→                <tr>\n    19→                    <td>{lineItem.itemId}</td>\n    20→                    <td>{lineItem.quantity}</td>\n    21→                    <td>{lineItem.vendorPart?.vendorPartNumber ?: 'N/A'}</td>\n    22→                </tr>\n    23→                {/for}\n    24→            </table>\n    25→            <br/>\n    26→            <table id=\"orderPartsTable\" rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n    27→                <tr>\n    28→                    <th>Part Number</th>\n    29→                    <th>Revision</th>\n    30→                    <th>Vendor Part Number</th>\n    31→                    <th>Add To Order</th>\n    32→                </tr>\n    33→                {#for part in newOrderParts}\n    34→                <tr>\n    35→                    <td>{part.partNumber}</td>\n    36→                    <td>{part.revision}</td>\n    37→                    <td>{part.vendorPart?.vendorPartNumber ?: 'N/A'}</td>\n    38→                    <td>\n    39→                        <form method=\"post\" action=\"/addLineItem\">\n    40→                            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"currentOrder\" value=\"{currentOrder}\"/>\n    41→                            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"selectedPartNumber\" value=\"{part.partNumber}\"/>\n    42→                            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"selectedPartRevision\" value=\"{part.revision}\"/>\n    43→                            <button type=\"submit\">Add</button>\n    44→                        </form>\n    45→                    </td>\n    46→                </tr>\n    47→                {/for}\n    48→            </table>\n    49→            <br/>\n    50→            <a href=\"/orders\">Back to Orders</a>\n    51→        </form>\n    52→        {/body}\n    53→    {/include}\n    54→</body>\n    55→</html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"380c2ee0-cd4b-46ce-87c8-68ac4fb04c36","uuid":"bfa0c680-8467-4abe-bb3b-e9acd33f4e10"}
